Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿敌奈落从我们的面前\N消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛这个强盗\N促成了奈落的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而与鬼蜘蛛\N曾经结盟的罗刹鬼勘助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临死之前又碰见了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一路打探\N奈落的行踪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也碰到了一个意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第88话 猿神大爷的三个小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子的气氛好祥和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子还没有被奈落糟蹋过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我总觉得这一带…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得什么  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么每块田\N都乱七八糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是野猪出来捣乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好像又不太像…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别走  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个银头发的年轻人请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你头上长了一对耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是在说犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你救救我们吧\N犬神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然叫你犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么犬神?在说我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点微薄的小菜不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在整个村里\N只剩下这点东西可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了犬神大爷之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想不出\N还有谁可以救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快用力扇  用力扇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然以为犬夜叉可以救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看恐怕拜错神了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个村子\N被那些猴子搞得一蹋糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得大家都没饭吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前的人不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子最怕的就是狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何\N犬神大爷一定要救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要\N帮我们赶走那些猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  这个忙我们帮定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  我哪里是什么犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶跑几只猴子一点都不难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们哪有那么多鬼时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟珊瑚会趁这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处打探奈落的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  这里的村民那么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会见死不救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是跟我开玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓猴子关我什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你是犬神大爷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是犬神大爷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只狗妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道我们最恨的就是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏替村民出头修理我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是这样\N这场戏还有什么看头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的就是对付妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小猴子哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  村子里的作物\N是你们糟蹋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是我们不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保证\N以后我们不会再犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这个精灵石交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  居然低声下气主动认错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再不收就不够意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么?七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你最好别太大意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们小妖最喜欢\N给别人东西然后再从中陷害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好还是别收下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛不早点说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该上当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只狗妖怪\N这下动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有见过\N猴子红红的屁股啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶作剧该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你再厉害也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你解得开我们的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然别想甩掉那块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?我倒要试试…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你们尝尝苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去追他们  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N你先在这边等我们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让他们跑掉了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刚刚他们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有施咒的人才解得开咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  弥勒法师我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是答应犬夜叉\N要到处打探奈落的消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在既没有\N鼻子超灵的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉得到\N四魂之玉碎片的戈薇也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才要不是那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想犬夜叉\N会乖乖帮那些村民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要振作起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁怕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟们  合体…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承让了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家快点过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要不要吃点心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么\N要糟蹋农夫伯伯的田地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在糟蹋那些田地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是在找\N被人类抓走的猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷\N本来是庙里供奉的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是\N猿神大爷身边的小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直帮大神看着寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便在那边修行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来因为战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺庙被烧光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷附身在里面的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道\N为什么会被人家偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这个村子里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们猜想\N猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被埋在田地里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为猿神大爷\N曾经托梦给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也梦见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有  我也梦过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷说 他被埋在\N一个又暗又湿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爷告诉我那个地方\N小得他都快喘不过气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷也跟我说\N他很怕闻到那些蔬菜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西在靠近我们耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐不骂你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先解开\N犬夜叉身上的咒语好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把咒语忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们再捣蛋下去\N小心会挨揍受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这家伙不管是大人小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要惹毛他都照打不误\N知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是故意捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的忘得一干二净了\N什么都记不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了你们\N等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找到猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒语自然就解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这些咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是\N猿神大爷他教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看还是尽快先回村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法找到神体再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好乖乖待在这边别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累不累啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我老待在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怜啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你变成什么样子了\N臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…你们两个臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把铁碎牙也耍不动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留给你太可惜了\N别碰我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我会帮你照顾戈薇的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙就由我做哥哥的\N替你保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  别走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不需要等到你们来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就在村子里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没听过啊  什么神体的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就赶到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好\N不要再跟我们装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到猿神大爷\N我们会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点还给我们\N还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不把大石头替我拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会宰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你动作还真快耶  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠那么近好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还想不出\N移开石头的咒语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几只小猴子\N就可以用法术把你困在石头上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是犬神大爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早说了\N是你们自己把我当成神的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实\N他离犬神大爷还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说只有猿神大爷\N才知道解咒的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你们继续隐瞒下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子早晚会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我安静一点不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看大家分头去找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续闹下去大家都会受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是像这么大的\N一块神圣的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面刻着猿神大爷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还圆滚滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后山山腰有一块像这样的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  就在后山是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在河边见过像这样的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块石头一点都不神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会在土地公那个林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是在东边地藏王旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看应该在南方山谷才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家屋檐下好像有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个马上\N给我去找猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开的期间\N就发生了这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试用我的法力\N看能不能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的可以\N帮我们找回猿神大爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在早上才能发挥作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想晚上\N找个地方好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下命捡回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全都上当啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚跟他们胡说八道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就一定可以想到办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得还是不太安心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真是没用哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这种法术困得动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕在这样下去会不可收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会不可收拾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去这只手\N就一直摆脱不了这颗石头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后没有办法再拿铁碎牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果犬夜叉就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直摆脱不了这颗石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让开  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂…“岩”爪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什么啊你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这样也不错啊   犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你又多了一项绝招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个臭家伙\N又在那边乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果犬夜叉一直摆脱不了石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以说走就走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死丫头  你也想到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我试着用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吸走这块大石头的话\N你说可行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以只吸这块大石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要力道控制得当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真的可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试打开风穴\N来吸走这块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你靠过来的时候风穴就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在叫什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你有一半的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在打什么鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会把你吸进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你先进屋子算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特地留下来陪我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你一个人待在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会很寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会寂寞啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌我烦那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有嫌你烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事还真是伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有没有别的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小地方\N就只有这种东西招待大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌菜怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是光芒是神光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些菜\N是从这边的菜园采的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是\N猿神大爷发出来的神光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷托梦告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在一个又暗又湿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方很小喘不过气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个有臭菜味的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子果然是埋在田里没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N是被埋在很深很深的土里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上把整个村子翻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  咻  嘿  咻\N不会又要作出那种事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有样东西\N想要请你让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这块腌菜用的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还闪闪发亮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是神体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我怎么看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然\N作出这么该死的事情来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来猿神大爷\N真的是你们偷走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头是我们在村外捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想拿来压腌菜缸刚好合用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指在森林之外的地方捡到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷一直好好的\N待在森林里面的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个小精灵\N看守得可仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 就连发生火灾那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是想尽办法\N誓死保护猿神大爷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把猿神大爷抬到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总该安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有松果耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有好多耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们自己\N把这件事情给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先用净水清洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你们好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于又见到您老人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些蔬菜臭死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个小家伙有没有不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我们全都很乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心把犬夜叉给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷\N要大家再帮他盖座新庙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定时祭拜他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就会保佑全村的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于摆脱那块石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无缘无故又在路上耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘你真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一下子\N就猜中我在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好的答谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您给我提示那么明显\N很容易就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个根本就是笨过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是\N口口声声说一定在田里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要大家赶快去挖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你们最好赶快离开这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到外边有点不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不寻常?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被放进腌菜缸之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然感觉到一股\N从没有遇到过的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股可怕的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从村子的上空飘过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷后来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么样的妖气\N我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在缸里还追踪过它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股妖气跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股妖气并没有走得太远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是很快地突然就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错  那一定是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖气是往丑寅方向移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是东北方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一点都感觉不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以决定\N接下来该往哪边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是松果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些死小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次报仇了  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也报仇了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个小家伙\N还挺好玩的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是还没有断奶的小猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好烦哦  走快点行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:20.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:29.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:39.20,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:49.20,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:54.12,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:59.02,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:06.45,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.00,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.17,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:24.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:34.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:41.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说戈薇病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近大家忙着寻找奈落\N把她给累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说不但感冒而且还发烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才急急忙忙的赶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该要不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们那边医药那么发达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想没问题\N应该很快就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又偷偷去找戈薇了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探病是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都看不出\N犬夜叉这小子这么体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉\N他和他之间的探病大战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和他?到底谁跟谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,从左到右分别是布 肯 贡{\pos(290,288)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在寻找\N猿神附身的精灵石{\pos(255,438)}
